Lotus Development Corp dey talk to sell im signal stockquoting service to Infotech Inc, di New York parent of Financial News Network, people wey be sey de don dey talk am.

Dem say di money go be around $10 million.

Signal wey get estimated 10,000 subscribers, and dey profitable, dey provide stock quotes on one FM radio band wey fit be specially equipped for personal computer.

Computers go dey show di price wey users dey select.

Letus, Cambridge, Mass. Dem don rumour sey dem go sell four years old unit for one year.

Di business no be sey na from Lotus main business wey be sey dey do computer program, and dey print information for compact disk.

